					 </revhistory> 
				</sect2info> 
				<title>Generic Dataphor File Types</title> 
				<para>Dataphor uses several different file types. Learn what they
					 are and what they contain in this section.</para> 
				<sect3 id="DCFFrontendSession"> 
					 <sect3info> 
						  <revhistory> 
								<revision> 
									 <revnumber>1</revnumber> 
									 <date>May 28, 2002 9:33:09 AM MDT</date> 
